SUMMARY:🎸 FolKloR — Street Festival | Bluegrass in La Roche 2026
DESCRIPTION:French acoustic folk trio from the Lyon and Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes region\, performing high-energy Celtic folk\, Irish music and American bluegrass. Simon Hel (also of Carban and Broken Bow) crosses bluegrass\, gypsy jazz and metal backgrounds; Perrine Bakubama brings classical\, Irish and Celtic fiddle; Kor Wentemn sings and plays guitar\, drawing on 60s-90s rock and folk. Members: Simon Hel (guitar)\, Perrine Bakubama (fiddle)\, Kor Wentemn (guitar/vocals) Le T'cho terrace\, town centre. FREE.
LOCATION:Le T'cho, 30 Imp. de l'Étang, 74800 La Roche-sur-Foron, France
END:VEVENT
