SUMMARY:🎸 Obejváci — Street Festival (Offsite) | Bluegrass in La Roche 2026
DESCRIPTION:Rising acoustic band from South Bohemia\, Czech Republic\, blending American-inspired bluegrass and folk with original Czech-language songwriting. Formed in 2021\, taking their name from the living room (obývák) where they first rehearsed. Debut EP Tisíc let (2024) followed by debut album Nebesák. Also showcased at the EBMA European Bluegrass Summit in Prague. Members: Kristýna Barchini (vocals/octave mandolin)\, Luboš Barchini (guitar/vocals)\, Jan Pelech (fiddle/vocals/mandolin)\, Petr Ježek (banjo)\, Štěpán Pavlíček (bass) EPSM (Établissement Public de Santé Mentale). Open to the public. FREE.
LOCATION:Etablissement Public de Santé Mentale (EPSM), 530 rue de la Patience, 74800 La Roche-sur-Foron, France
END:VEVENT
