SUMMARY:🎸 Blue Morning Train — Street Festival | Bluegrass in La Roche 2026
DESCRIPTION:French acoustic string band playing traditional American Bluegrass and roots music\, touring extensively across Europe. Members: Philippe Boutet (guitar/lead vocals)\, Joël Amar (fiddle/vocals)\, Hervé Lascaux (banjo/mandolin)\, Isabelle Lascaux (double bass) Bistro Tokyo terrace\, town centre. FREE.
