SUMMARY:🎸 Karoline & the Free Folks — Street Festival | Bluegrass in La Roche 2026
DESCRIPTION:Lyon-based Americana/country-bluegrass project led by singer-guitarist Karoline\, drawing on Brandi Carlile\, Trey Hensley and the Allman Brothers. Debut album Reckless Dances (2022) was followed by Blooming Haze. Performs as full amplified quartet or in stripped-back acoustic formats. Noor Jahan terrace\, town centre. FREE.
LOCATION:Noor Jahan, 121 rue Carnot, 74800 La Roche-sur-Foron, France
