SUMMARY:🎸 Strawberry Moon — Street Festival | Bluegrass in La Roche 2026
DESCRIPTION:French-American acoustic duo reimagining old-time\, folk and bluegrass with original songwriting and rich vocal harmonies\, bringing a modern feminist perspective to American roots music. Active on the European acoustic circuit\, with performances at venues including The Art Café Lagny and Le Piano Vache (Paris)\, and at the Gloryland Festival. Members: Anaëlle Trumka (vocals/banjo/fiddle)\, Lucia Legnini (vocals/guitar) Le Petit Café terrace\, town centre. FREE.
LOCATION:Le Petit Café, 31 Rue Carnot, 74800 La Roche-sur-Foron, France
